        content: 'Maine DMR samples shellfish growing areas on schedules that vary by classification: Approved areas weekly during growing season + biweekly in winter. Restricted areas more frequent. Conditional areas: rainfall-triggered closures. Sample types: water bacteriological (coliform), biotoxin (PSP, DSP, ASP). Lab turnaround typically 24-72 hr. Closure decisions based on rolling averages + thresholds.',
